### Test Plant Categories Endpoint (for troubleshooting 415 error)

### 1. Get Plant Categories (GET request - should work)
GET https://localhost:7051/api/plantcategories
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###

### 2. Get Plant Categories (alternative endpoint if the above fails)
GET https://localhost:7051/api/PlantCategories
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###

### 3. Test Multi-Inspection Items (POST request)
POST https://localhost:7051/api/multiinspection/items
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "customerId": 1,
    "categoryIds": [1, 2]
}

###

### 4. Test with minimal data to isolate the issue
POST https://localhost:7051/api/multiinspection/items
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "customerId": 1,
    "categoryIds": []
}

###

### 5. Check if the API is running and accessible
GET https://localhost:7051/api/status
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

###

### 6. Test without auth (to see if it's an auth issue)
POST https://localhost:7051/api/multiinspection/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "customerId": 1,
    "categoryIds": [1]
}

